reviews.review_text:
Food served here is way better than the restaurants in Goa.
Despite the ambience, We used to go for lunch & dinner at this restaurant as it is economical (had tummy full food for 4 people and never crossed 1k)and tastes good.
We Tried chicken crispy and chicken fried rice and loved it, also the food portions are comparatively more.

Veru good food and very quick service
Must try squids rava fry and chicken crispy.
The place is nice with good food and service but lacks the photogenic environment very dull , they should put some lighting and decoration so it stands out overall a very good restaurant .
